author: Adam Brewster
title: Wisconsin voters to go to the polls Tuesday, despite "stay-home" order
description: The dispute over absentee voting in Wisconsin is the first stemming from the coronavirus pandemic to reach the U.S. Supreme Court.
content: Under a statewide "safer-at-home" order intended to prevent more widespread COVID-19 infection, Wisconsinites are going to the polls to vote in person Tuesday, after a series of legal battles over whether or not the primary election could be delayed and wheth… [+3463 chars]
